<BaseLayout title="Our Mission - Phoebe Dawson Foundation" currentPath="/mission">
    <!-- ============ PAGE HERO ============ -->
    <section class="page-hero">
        <img src="/assets/group.jpg" alt="Team WWPD">
        <div class="page-hero-overlay">
            <h1>Our Mission</h1>
            <p class="page-hero-subtitle">Carrying Phoebe's Legacy Forward</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ MISSION STATEMENT ============ -->
    <section class="mission-statement">
        <div class="mission-statement-content">
            <p class="lead">The Phoebe Dawson Foundation was established in late 2025 to honour the vibrant legacy of our "sunshine girl," Phoebe Dawson.</p>
            <p>Phoebe was a woman of "big life energy" who lived with immense empathy, discovering her vocation for helping others while working in a remote village medical center in Kenya. Throughout her distinguished career as a nurse, she served on the frontlines of respiratory and oncology units, supported the COVID-19 vaccination effort, and helped patients access life-changing technologies.</p>
            <p>Tragically lost in early 2024, Phoebe's spirit continues to radiate through the work of this Foundation. Our mission is to raise funds and awareness for charities and organisations that reflect Phoebe's passion for frontline health support, nursing excellence, and practical innovations in patient care.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

